Name: Average resolution time for 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time difference between 'Accepted + In Progress' and 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total time spent in 'Completed + Cancelled' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Minimum time to reach 'Completed + Cancelled' from 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time from 'Completed + In Call' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total resolution time of 'Completed + Cancelled' compared to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Minimum resolution time of 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time it takes to transition from 'Accepted + Wait - User' to 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time from 'Completed + Cancelled' to the next activity in the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Time until 'Completed + Cancelled' from case initiation
Metric: The average of the duration between the start of the case and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average waiting time to 'Completed + Cancelled' after 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Total time it takes 'Completed + Cancelled' to be done after 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Minimum time between 'Completed + In Call' and 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Average time difference between 'Completed + Cancelled' and all other activities in the event log
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Completed + Cancelled and the end of the case

Name: Total time for 'Completed + Cancelled' in comparison to the total time for 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Completed + Resolved' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Time of 'Completed + Cancelled' cycle in comparison to 'Completed + In Call' cycle time
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Completed + In Call' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'
